			<div class="w-full md:w-auto mx-auto md:mx-2 text-center">Made with &hearts; (and a smidge of AI) in Kansas City.</div>
			<div class="w-full md:w-auto mx-auto md:mx-2 text-center">Source available on <a href="https://github.com/BeSublime/cardfork">GitHub</a>.</div>
